name: Number 76: Gladiyell the Melody Lumaestra
desc:
2 Level 7 monsters
While face-up on the field, this card is also the Attributes of its materials. Cannot be destroyed by battle with a monster with the same Attribute as this card, also cannot be destroyed by activated effects from an opponent's monster with the same Attribute as this card. (Quick Effect): You can target 1 monster in your opponent's GY; detach 1 material from this card, and if you do, attach that monster to this card as material. You can only use this effect of "Number 76: Gladiyell the Melody Lumaestra" once per turn.
str1: Attach 1 monster from the opponent's GY
